@startuml
client -> ClientHttpRequestInterceptor: apply
ClientHttpRequestInterceptor -> HttpRequestContextInterceptor:
HttpRequestContextInterceptor -> HttpRequestContextInterceptor: setOutContext\n(从threadLocal取出\n标签,并设置到http 头)
HttpRequestContextInterceptor -> IRule:
IRule -> RuleInterceptor:
RuleInterceptor -> RemoteServer:choose\n(据标签匹配实例)
RemoteServer -> WebContextInterceptor:
WebContextInterceptor->WebContextInterceptor:setInContext\n(n把标签设置到threadLocal)
WebContextInterceptor-> BusinessService:invoke(调用业务代码)
WebContextInterceptor-->WebContextInterceptor:clear(清除标签)
WebContextInterceptor-->RemoteServer
RemoteServer-->RuleInterceptor
RuleInterceptor-->IRule
IRule-->HttpRequestContextInterceptor
HttpRequestContextInterceptor-->ClientHttpRequestInterceptor
